===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
A compound of {{Han compound|人|凡|巾|t1=person|t3=piece of cloth}}. Original meaning is a large sash.

The role of {{och-l|*凡}} is unclear. Some think that it is a phonetic component, but the finals differ substantially (compare {{och-l|凡}} to {{och-l|佩}}).<ref>{{R:yue:Hanzi}}</ref>

